_sText:
This map was originally going to be 2 long stages, but turned into a linear map.
It has around 1 minute surfing.
It has a 5 minute timer, if nobody beats the map before the timer goes off, you will get teleported to jail and be given a knife.


Thank you to the testers.
Thank you to Justin.uk and Pand3mic for helping.
